data.description: This charming 3 bedroom, 1 bathroom ranch nestled in the heart of Royal Oak is is ready for immediate occupancy by its new owner(s)! Step inside to be greeted by the beautiful hardwood floors and fresh paint throughout the home. The kitchen has been recently upgraded with BRAND NEW stainless steel appliances and luxury vinyl wood flooring. Additionally, the first-level convenient laundry area features a new gas supply line, water heater, HVAC and furnace. You'll also appreciate the newly remodeled entryway leading to a rare attached 2 doors garage, which now features brand new walls, ceiling and garage doors! Additional updates made to this home include new electric outlets, copper and PVC plumbing and ductwork throughout enhancing its efficiency and providing peace of mind to the new owner for years to come. Combined with its countless upgrades and prime location in Royal Oak, this ranch is one you don't want to miss!
